name: Gran Surya Hotel & Waterpark Bali
address: Jl. Sudirman No.11, Seririt, Kec. Seririt, Kabupaten Buleleng, Bali 81153, Indonesia
review 1:
The first time stay in this hotel, stayed in executive room which we expect will be the best room, however we found poor of cleanliness inside the room, dirty bed sheet, a lot. of hairs in the floor, found a spider web inside the bathroom, dirty fridge, etc. Luckily Manager showed up and apologize and took action through the staff. Beside staff was friendly and helpful.
Note: more detail to cleanliness
review 2: First impressions was like horor place until we check in. Once you are in the room you feel the different, room is clean, comfort bed room and clean sheet, bathroom also clean, clean towel. Friendly staff and big parking space. They have very nice waterpark and free entrance (hotel provide voucher) for hotel guest. Recommended
review 3:
Nice hotel to stay, but during the pandemic many of facilities are closed.
Hope this pandemic will over soon, so the hotel will back live again.
Please like this review if you think this review is helpful
review 4: Room was quite big, but after pandemic service must be increased...Hot water got normally after complain.
review 5: Good hotel with adequate rooms.  The Gran Surya Water park is right next door and our four year old son loved it! Two adult tickets are usually included with the  room.
